data.text:
Our famous wings are exactly what wing enthusiasts want. They’re crispy, juicy, and always fresh.

Our tender and juicy boneless wings are fried to perfection. Tossed in one of our famous sauces, these beauties will hit the spot.

Craving more than wings?! Our sandwich line-up is no joke. Buffalo favorites like beef on weck and our Duff’s style grilled cheese are always crowd pleasers, while our burgers are second to none!

If you’re in the mood for greens, we’ve got you covered at Duff’s. We’ve got a wide variety of fresh, made to order salads and wraps for you to indulge in!
